metadata.name: Mad King of Mars
metadata.description:
The Mad King of Mars is a painting featuring the King of Mars “MUSK” , who is ruling Mars in an alternate universe. Musk known for building advanced kingdoms on Martian planes in an attempt to conquer his enemies.

Main goal  of him is to conquer the Mars  and take control of it  and eventually build new kingdoms on every other planet He is also known to be very paranoid about keeping secrets from others so he never told anyone what he was planning until it was too late!

He has built an advanced kingdom, with a beautiful city and luxurious lifestyle for his subjects. He has even began to bring people from Earth to live with him in this new society.

However, there is one problem: he is missing something vital for any king to succeed in his task: Love
